                    <span>I normally don't write reviews. Couple of not very positive reviews could not stop me writing one for this title. In my opinion, this book really presents a breadth of information<br>on the subject. If one is considering to buy this book, one should have due background in Discrete Mathematics.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Terrible book</div>
